    <text x="40" y="118" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Approach: single, binding rulebook</text>
    <text x="40" y="146" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Scope: applies to all 27 member states</text>
    <text x="40" y="174" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Enforcement: direct EU-body supervision</text>
    <text x="40" y="202" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13">Speed: legally binding on taking effect</text>
    <text x="40" y="242" fill="#7dd3fc" font-size="13" font-weight="700">Pro: predictable, immediate force</text>
    <text x="40" y="266" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Con: takes time to reach 27-nation</text>
    <text x="40" y="290" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">consensus, less flexible</text>
